## Test Analysis

### Test: `DisplayAttributeTakesPrecedenceOverDisplayNameAttribute`
The test expects `[Display]` to take precedence over `[DisplayName]`. The test model has:
```csharp
[Display(Name = "Display Takes Precedence")]
